--- !u!114 &7256786141335147897
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 4684106143123002192}
  m_Enabled: 0
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 23b7a675a0ce8aa4386f21ae1b276b0e, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::DialoguesManager
  dialogues:
  - dialogueName: Start
    dialogues:
    - side: 0
      who: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 11946e27dd0e85f45a743944aa4b6485, type: 2}
      text: According to the villagers around here is where there is more attacks
    - side: 0
      who: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 11946e27dd0e85f45a743944aa4b6485, type: 2}
      text: Well, i also followed the lightings and explosion...
    - side: 0
      who: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 11946e27dd0e85f45a743944aa4b6485, type: 2}
      text: But enought wating the time, i have to resolve this.
    currentText: 0
  - dialogueName: Boss
    dialogues:
    - side: 1
      who: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 6ab7f228d4a12fa4ebbdd32bcc919082, type: 2}
      text: Ok, who is the one that is killing my servants
    - side: 0
      who: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 11946e27dd0e85f45a743944aa4b6485, type: 2}
      text: oh, so you are who is leading the attack
    - side: 1
      who: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 6ab7f228d4a12fa4ebbdd32bcc919082, type: 2}
      text: Of course, who you tough would be if isnt me, the new queen of the fairies
        <color="red">Mih <color="white">.
    - side: 0
      who: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 11946e27dd0e85f45a743944aa4b6485, type: 2}
      text: Uhm... Who?
    - side: 1
      who: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 6ab7f228d4a12fa4ebbdd32bcc919082, type: 2}
      text: ...
    - side: 1
      who: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 6ab7f228d4a12fa4ebbdd32bcc919082, type: 2}
      text: So you dont know who am i?\nWell, too bad for you then, once i kill you,
        you will know how powerful i am!
    currentText: 0
  - dialogueName: AfterBoss
    dialogues:
    - side: 1
      who: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 6ab7f228d4a12fa4ebbdd32bcc919082, type: 2}
      text: Ugh... how?...\nI have to be the strongest, how can a child defeat me
    - side: 1
      who: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 6ab7f228d4a12fa4ebbdd32bcc919082, type: 2}
      text: He gave me all this power for nothing...
    - side: 0
      who: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 11946e27dd0e85f45a743944aa4b6485, type: 2}
      text: Hey, why did you attack the village? \nMaybe i can spare you if you cooperate
    - side: 1
      who: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 6ab7f228d4a12fa4ebbdd32bcc919082, type: 2}
      text: Power, what else would it be? \nI have to show everyone who is the most
        powerfull queen here.
    - side: 0
      who: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 11946e27dd0e85f45a743944aa4b6485, type: 2}
      text: Then i heard you said someone gave you that power, who is he?
    - side: 1
      who: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 6ab7f228d4a12fa4ebbdd32bcc919082, type: 2}
      text: Seems the child dont stop asking question. \nBut even if i wanted i cant
        said that, you know how powerful can be a contract and the punishments of
        break it.
    - side: 1
      who: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 6ab7f228d4a12fa4ebbdd32bcc919082, type: 2}
      text: The only thing i can tell you is to be careful with the river. I heard
        isnt that calm that before.
    - side: 0
      who: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 11946e27dd0e85f45a743944aa4b6485, type: 2}
      text: The river? Whats wrong with the river?
    - side: 1
      who: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 11946e27dd0e85f45a743944aa4b6485, type: 2}
      text: ...?
    - side: 1
      who: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 11946e27dd0e85f45a743944aa4b6485, type: 2}
      text: ...?
    currentText: 0
